---
title: Pork Jägerschnitzel & Creamy Mushroom Sauce with Potato Mash & Apple Salad
description: Jägerschnitzel, a hearty German delight, pairs tender breaded pork with a rich mushroom sauce that's perfect for a cozy feast
for the adults. Drizzle over a simple creamy sauce for the kids, without the mushrooms if they're not a fan. Potato mash soaks up
extra sauce, and acts as the ideal accompaniment for this dreamy combo!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66580c627380bbe91ab402d0-4a704698.jpeg
